1
00:00:00,010 --> 00:00:01,350
前情提要

2
00:00:01,380 --> 00:00:02,820
趴下! 所有人趴下!
Down! Everybody down!

3
00:00:02,850 --> 00:00:04,750
解放组织洗劫那些保险柜
Liber8 is fishing for something specific

4
00:00:04,790 --> 00:00:06,320
是为了寻找一样特别的东西
in those safety deposit boxes.

5
00:00:06,350 --> 00:00:07,220
怎么回事?
What's happening?

6
00:00:07,250 --> 00:00:08,960
首先 我打赌这是一个全新的战斗策略
First, I bet a whole new battle strategy.

7
00:00:08,990 --> 00:00:11,690
一年来你一直秘密使用这张SIM卡?
You used the same secret SIM card for a year?

8
00:00:11,730 --> 00:00:13,130
解放组织给我下了套...
Liber8 wanted me on the hook and...

9
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:15,360
省省吧 贝蒂
Save it, Betty.

10
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:17,100
我们要拿你做诱饵
We're going to use you as bait.

11
00:00:17,130 --> 00:00:19,030
你真觉得他们肯乖乖的把你捧作
Did you really think they were gonna let you play Steve Jobs

12
00:00:19,070 --> 00:00:20,270
史蒂夫·乔布斯吗?
without a fight?

13
00:00:20,300 --> 00:00:22,640
你得跟他们硬碰硬才行
You need a shark to take on these sharks.

14
00:00:22,670 --> 00:00:23,970
离艾力克远一点
Stay away from Alec.

15
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,200
哪一个艾力克?
Which one?

16
00:00:25,240 --> 00:00:27,310
我猜咱们两个是没法做朋友了 对吗?
So I guess we're not gonna be pals then, huh?

17
00:00:27,340 --> 00:00:29,340
我也这样想
I don't see how.

18
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:38,820
别忘记做作业 帝奥
Don't forget to do your homework, Tio.

19
00:00:38,850 --> 00:00:41,990
妈妈 我讨厌算分数
Mom, I hate fractions.

20
00:00:42,020 --> 00:00:45,960
我也是 但你不练习考试就会不及格
So did I, but you won't pass your exams without them.

21
00:00:49,460 --> 00:00:51,430
帝奥 我不是叫你把门关上了吗?
Tio, I thought I told you to close the door?

22
00:00:58,070 --> 00:01:00,500
爹地!
Daddy!

23
00:01:00,540 --> 00:01:02,340
嘿!
Hey!

24
00:01:02,370 --> 00:01:03,840
我想死你了!
I missed you so much!

25
00:01:04,880 --> 00:01:06,910
你去哪儿了?
Where have you been?

26
00:01:06,950 --> 00:01:08,880
我的生日你都错过了
You missed my birthday.

27
00:01:08,910 --> 00:01:11,250
我也不想的 宝贝
I didn't want to, baby.

28
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,380
嘿!
Hey!

29
00:01:12,420 --> 00:01:14,420
爹地不应该回来的
Daddy knows he shouldn't be here.

30
00:01:14,450 --> 00:01:15,920
我们说过的安全第一
We talked about staying safe.

31
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:17,620
我另有办法
I have another way.

32
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:21,330
去玩吧 去
Go play. Go.

33
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,600
她的DNA是伪造的
Her DNA is forged.

34
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:26,200
万一被发现是你这种人的女儿...
If they find out that she's the daughter of a..

35
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:27,330
哪种人? 逃亡者?
A fugitive?

36
00:01:27,370 --> 00:01:29,400
恐怖分子?
A terrorist?

37
00:01:29,430 --> 00:01:32,500
你不会真的相信吧
You don't believe that.

38
00:01:32,540 --> 00:01:34,540
我怎么想又没有用
It doesn't matter what I believe.

39
00:01:34,570 --> 00:01:35,810
当我无比渴望跟你们相聚的时候
Belief is the only thing that keeps me going

40
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,940
信念是唯一支撑我走下去的力量
when I'm dying to be with you both.

41
00:01:37,980 --> 00:01:40,780
我是说 帝奥需要知道信念是...
I mean, Tio needs to learn that belief is...

42
00:01:43,820 --> 00:01:48,120
当你偷听别人说话时信念就会是个问题!
belief is only a problem when you're eavesdropping!

43
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:50,150
让你尝尝我的厉害!
Because this is what happens!

44
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,480
去右边!!!
To the right!!

45
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:16,710
右边!!!
On the right!!!

46
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:19,280
进去 进去!!!
In, in, in!!!!

47
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:21,380
那边有人
There.

48
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:23,650
搜查完毕
Clear.

49
00:02:23,690 --> 00:02:25,250
没有发现 长官
All clear sir.

50
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:40,370
这儿仍然残留着他的信息素
His pheromone levels are still ambient.

51
00:02:43,410 --> 00:02:46,610
为了自己着想 你们两个说实话吧
It's better for the both of you if you were to tell the truth.

52
00:02:49,650 --> 00:02:51,810
你们跟他有什么关系?
What's your connection to him?

53
00:02:51,850 --> 00:02:52,650
你搞错了
Please.

54
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,280
他刚刚还威胁要杀了我们
He threatened to kill us.

55
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,650
我们都是好公民
We're good citizens.

56
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,350
忠于国家
We're loyal.

57
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:05,130
那你呢 小甜心?
And what about you, sweetheart?

58
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:09,130
你忠于企业集团议会吗?
Are you loyal to the corporate congress?

59
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:13,030
我已经在学校立过誓言了
I took the oath in school.

60
00:03:13,070 --> 00:03:16,400
你不希望妈妈有麻烦吧 对不对?
You want to help your mother out, don't you?

61
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:21,270
那就说实话 他去哪儿了?
So tell me, where did he go?

62
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:37,990
贝尔塔 下来吧
Verta, down.

63
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:39,890
立刻
Now.

64
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:44,100
瞄准他了!
I got him!

65
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:47,170
下来
Get down.

66
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:49,240
快点下来!!!
Get down now!!!

67
00:03:52,970 --> 00:03:54,610
慢点
Easy.

68
00:04:00,910 --> 00:04:03,010
跪下!
Down on your knees!

69
00:04:46,020 --> 00:04:49,020
超越时间线 第三季第五集 三十分钟直播

70
00:05:14,150 --> 00:05:15,100
照片标签上就写
Hash-tag

71
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:16,390
"亲我的屁屁 弗门塔斯"怎么样?
"kiss my ass Fermitas"?

72
00:05:16,390 --> 00:05:18,020
经典!
Epic!

73
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:32,020
弗门塔斯 助纣为虐

74
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:43,480
这公司的保安干什么吃的
The corporate security was primitive at best.

75
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,810
那些抗议者应该连大厅
Those protesters never should have made it

76
00:05:44,850 --> 00:05:46,080
都进不去才对
past the lobby.

77
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:49,150
他们为什么瞄准弗门塔斯?
Why paint a bullseye on Fermitas?

78
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:51,520
你的用词还真是讽刺啊
Well, that's an ironic choice of words.

79
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:54,190
弗门塔斯是世界上最大的军火制造商之一
Fermitas is one of the world's largest weapons manufacturers,

80
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:57,030
就像军火界的沃尔玛
like the Wal-Mart for warlords.

81
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,390
你在跟这个案子吗?
You chasing this one down?

82
00:05:58,430 --> 00:06:00,230
非法入室和示威抗议?
Trespassing and opinionated protests?

83
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:02,360
还真不是我的工作范围
It's not really my department.

84
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:04,730
在我看来是解放组织的煽动行为
It seems to me like Liber8's recruiting methods

85
00:06:04,770 --> 00:06:06,670
终于起作用了
are paying off.

86
00:06:06,700 --> 00:06:08,500
非暴力抗议早在你的朋友
Civil disobedience has been around

87
00:06:08,540 --> 00:06:10,470
出现之前就有了
long before your friends showed up.

88
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:13,740
卡洛斯?
Carlos?

89
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:22,350
我们都是长途跋涉走到今天
We've both travelled long distances,

90
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:26,120
见过很多他人闻所未闻的事情
seen things other people can't know or understand.

91
00:06:26,150 --> 00:06:28,290
我们可以互相帮助
We could help each other.

92
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:31,690
我们已经是一路人马了 你还想怎样?
We're already on the same team, what more do you want?

93
00:06:31,730 --> 00:06:34,100
每个人都需要伙伴
Everyone needs a partner.

94
00:06:34,130 --> 00:06:35,330
卡洛斯和艾力克...
Carlos, Alec...

95
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,200
你们的友谊正在分崩离析
Those relationships are fracturing.

96
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:42,700
凯瑟琳知道你来找我吗?
Does Katherine know you're here?

97
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:45,070
是她要我关照你的
She asked me to keep an eye on you.

98
00:06:45,110 --> 00:06:48,610
这可算不上是个回答
That is not an answer.

99
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:51,910
也许他只是在向你表示善意
It's possible his offer was a gesture of goodwill.

100
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:54,950
他的字典里可没有"善意"这个词
Goodwill is not in his arsenal.

101
00:06:54,980 --> 00:06:56,580
我不信任他
I don't trust him.

102
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:58,890
他知道我敬重你 也知道我们有交流
Well, he knows I respect you and he knows we talk,

103
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:01,720
也许他的动机就是这么简单
so maybe that's all it is.

104
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:05,030
但你能告诉我这些我很感激
I appreciate you telling me, though.

105
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:07,830
这里的大部分人都没有家人
Most of the people in this cell don't have families.

106
00:07:07,860 --> 00:07:10,530
他们在传统社会中没有立足之地
They found themselves lost in traditional society.

107
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,330
其中一些是我从街上收进来的
Some I recruited off the streets,

108
00:07:12,370 --> 00:07:15,070
其他的则是主动投奔而来
others found their way to me.

109
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:18,100
他们中的很多人都缺乏母爱
For many of them, mother-less.

110
00:07:18,140 --> 00:07:20,310
我填补了这个角色
I can fulfil that roll.

111
00:07:23,010 --> 00:07:25,880
你对当前的局势怎么看?
How do things feel to you?

112
00:07:25,910 --> 00:07:29,850
解放组织自从银行抢劫案之后就悄无声息
Liber8 has been quiet since the bank robberies.

113
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:33,190
各方势力也没有动静
All that energy in theatre to little or no effect.

114
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:35,220
你也有这样的感觉?
You feel that?

115
00:07:35,260 --> 00:07:36,560
某种程度上是的
In a way.

116
00:07:36,590 --> 00:07:38,020
你不也是吗?
Don't you?

117
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:43,630
那里面是什么?
What's in there?

118
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:53,140
很高兴你来了
I'm glad you're here.

119
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,590
好吧 如果我不接
Okay, if I don't answer this,

120
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:06,990
卢卡斯会起疑心的
Lucas is going to wonder why.

121
00:08:07,030 --> 00:08:08,760
你觉得我会蠢到让你给他
You think I'm gonna let you send him some kind of message

122
00:08:08,790 --> 00:08:09,930
通风报信吗?
by the way you answer?

123
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:10,960
不许接
No.

124
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,660
我会按你们的要求接电话
I will answer it any way you want.

125
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:14,070
他不常打电话给我的
He doesn't call that often.

126
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:15,830
我说过了不行
I said no.

127
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:20,940
如果她是对的怎么办?
What if she's right?

128
00:08:20,970 --> 00:08:24,210
我们来决定什么时候拿她当诱饵
We'll pick the moment to use her to our advantage.

129
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,140
按我们的方式
On our terms.

130
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:32,380
嘿 你去哪儿了?
Hey, where've you been?

131
00:08:32,420 --> 00:08:34,920
碰到了一个老朋友
I ran into an old friend.

132
00:08:34,950 --> 00:08:36,750
有意思 我都不知道你还有老朋友
Funny, I wasn't aware you had any of those.

133
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,490
怎么回事?
What is it?

134
00:08:43,260 --> 00:08:46,600
这个地方从来都不能消停一下
This department just can't catch a break.

135
00:08:49,470 --> 00:08:51,530
强行入室罪
Break and enter.

136
00:08:51,570 --> 00:08:53,200
非法侵入罪
Criminal trespass.

137
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,700
怠忽致危罪
Reckless endangerment.

138
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:56,140
直接叫我恐怖分子好了
Just call me a terrorist.

139
00:08:56,170 --> 00:08:59,510
反正在你眼里都是一个样
That's what we all are to you.

140
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:00,060
当着两位证人
This is being recorded

141
00:09:00,060 --> 00:09:01,940
卡梅伦探员和福乃格探长的面
in front of two witnesses,

142
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:04,680
以下对话将记录在案
Agent Cameron and Detective Fonnegra.

143
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:08,480
我确定你刚才的话只是讽刺 无其他含义
I will stipulate that you were being sarcastic just then.

144
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,850
视网膜扫描 心跳正常
不要再犯这样的错误
Don't repeat that mistake.

145
00:09:09,890 --> 00:09:11,020
接下来 继续记录再案
Now, for the record,

146
00:09:11,050 --> 00:09:13,620
你已经了解了你的权利
you've already been advised of your rights.

147
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:14,920
我们的行为是无害的
What we did was harmless.

148
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,130
没有人受伤
Nobody got hurt.

149
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,690
你的所作所为已经够得上起诉了
What you did is an indictable offense!

150
00:09:17,730 --> 00:09:19,730
那是要坐牢的
You could serve time.

151
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:21,100
现在我想知道为什么
Now I want to know why.

152
00:09:21,130 --> 00:09:22,590
狮门大学被血洗之后
Do I really have to say it

153
00:09:22,590 --> 00:09:23,670
原因不是显而易见吗?
after the bloodbath at LGU?

154
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:25,270
我是在表明立场
I'm taking a stand.

155
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:26,840
那次射杀 还有之后你的做法...
That shooting, your tactics...

156
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:29,900
用于应对威胁是必要 且适度的
Were necessary and proportionate to the threat.

157
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,780
告诉我你要请律师
Tell me you want a lawyer.

158
00:09:37,810 --> 00:09:40,250
不是吧 老爸
You can't be serious, dad.

159
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:42,780
克里斯汀 我只能帮你到这儿了
Christine, this is as far as I am willing to stretch.

160
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:45,490
现在 快说
Now, say the words.

161
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,930
给我找个律师
I want a lawyer.

162
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:01,270
好吧 刚才那一幕我们可没有办法完全
Well, we're not going to be able to sweep that one

163
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:02,500
隐瞒过去
under the rug.

164
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:04,100
如果她免于被起诉的话 他和整个部门都会被
If she isn't charged, it puts him and the whole department

165
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:05,670
都将被推上风口浪尖
under a microscope.

166
00:10:05,710 --> 00:10:07,780
这又不是她一个人做的
She didn't do this on her own.

167
00:10:07,810 --> 00:10:09,910
哦 没错啊 他们都有罪哦
Oh yeah, sure, they're both guilty.

168
00:10:09,940 --> 00:10:12,110
但是其他孩子不会上头条
But that other kid's not gonna lead the news.

169
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:13,780
他们才会
They are.

170
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:16,220
不管怎么运作 这都是一个两败俱伤的结果
This is lose-lose any way you play it.

171
00:10:18,290 --> 00:10:20,890
我觉得你还少说了一个
I think you're one "lose" short.

172
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:23,190
我是不是需要个工会代表?
Do I need my union rep?

173
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:25,160
这又不是在审问你 杰克
There's no inquisition here, Jack.

174
00:10:25,190 --> 00:10:28,200
是还没...
Yet...

175
00:10:28,230 --> 00:10:30,200
你女儿支持解放组织
You're daughter is pro Liber8.

176
00:10:30,230 --> 00:10:32,470
你认为这事会怎样?
How do you think that looks?

177
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:35,970
听你的意思 是不是又要逼我辞职了?
Is this the part where I clear out my desk again?

178
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,470
我监督你的工作
Just because I'm your oversight

179
00:10:37,510 --> 00:10:39,240
并不代表我不支持你的工作
doesn't mean I'm not your advocate.

180
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,940
你知道是谁在资助我
You know who I'm funded by.

181
00:10:40,970 --> 00:10:42,180
很了解
Intimately.

182
00:10:42,210 --> 00:10:47,010
那你就应该清楚我这次可没有那么容易就被挤走
Then you realize I won't be removed as easily as last time.

183
00:10:47,050 --> 00:10:49,680
在这件事儿上 我们有可以合作的空间
I think that there's room for cooperation.

184
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:52,720
我们互利互惠嘛
Every back needs scratching.

185
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:55,190
你现在有什么主意吗?
What did you have in mind?

186
00:10:55,220 --> 00:10:57,190
引导舆论
Spin.

187
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:17,080
这事儿我帮不了她
I can't save her from this.

