She's gonna lead the news, Niky.

195
00:11:28,490 --> 00:11:30,590
我所能做的就是把她和其他孩子一样看待
The only thing I can do is treat her like any other kid.

196
00:11:30,620 --> 00:11:31,560
那不一样!
She's not!

197
00:11:31,590 --> 00:11:32,790
必须这样
She has to be.

198
