There was a time you believed in them, too.

204
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:50,170
我现在也是
I still do.

205
00:11:50,210 --> 00:11:52,680
克里斯必将被追究责任的
Chrissy will be held accountable.

206
00:11:56,780 --> 00:11:57,920
