We both know that I'm not unique.

233
00:13:24,230 --> 00:13:26,370
你在逗我?
You're kidding me?

234
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:29,640
你他妈的可是能创造未来的人啊
You're the damn architect of the future.

235
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,480
按照目前赛德科技发展来看
