Nigel, can you believe this?

272
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,240
当然不可能了
No, absolutely not.

273
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:21,010
狄龙警官只有对企业集团的大佬们
Inspector Dillon is answerable

274
00:15:21,050 --> 00:15:22,550
才会表现出负责的态度
only to his corporate overlords,

275
00:15:22,580 --> 00:15:25,220
