certainly not the people and not the city.

276
00:15:25,250 --> 00:15:27,350
现在的问题是我的女儿需要对谁负责
This is about who my daughter answers to.

277
00:15:27,390 --> 00:15:29,920
她的行为很严重 一定会被起诉
It's a serious offense and she will be held accountable.

278
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:31,320
是初犯吧?
A first offense?

279
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:33,060
换做任何一个父母都会想方设法
Any parent can understand wanting to use whatever

280
00:15:33,090 --> 00:15:34,360
利用任何可能...
influence they could...

281
00:15:34,390 --> 00:15:35,830
戴安娜 我不像普通家长
Diana, I don't get to be any parent.

282
00:15:35,860 --> 00:15:37,860
我的责任是二十四小时全天候的
My accountability is 24/7.

283
00:15:37,900 --> 00:15:40,230
而且 很不幸 对我女儿来讲 由于血缘关系
And, unfortunately for my daughter, by association,

284
00:15:40,260 --> 00:15:41,500
她的也是
hers is too.

285
00:15:41,530 --> 00:15:44,070
在你的职责之下已经出现过丑闻 警方掩盖真相
Under your accountability we've had scandals, police cover-ups

286
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:45,570
两位市长身亡这样的事情
and two dead mayors.

287
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,270
警长 你说说看
Inspector, tell us:

288
00:15:46,270 --> 00:15:47,600
如果你不是警察 你女儿现在的情况
How would your daughter's situation

289
00:15:47,640 --> 00:15:49,710
会出现多大的改观吗?
play out different if you weren't a cop?

290
00:15:49,740 --> 00:15:51,410
如果我不是警察?
If I wasn't a cop?

291
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:53,010
那就没什么可讲的了 对吧?
There wouldn't be a story, would there?

292
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:54,440
所以你打算将为非作歹的女儿
So you're gonna let the system

293
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:56,610
直接移交司法部门处理?
take care of your miscreant daughter?

294
00:15:56,650 --> 00:15:58,880
法律系统就是这样运作的 没错
That's how the justice system works, yes.

295
00:15:58,920 --> 00:16:01,380
那这是否也适用于你的私人警备枪杀
Does that include your own private police

296
00:16:01,420 --> 00:16:04,190
无辜的大学生呢?
shooting innocent university students?

297
00:16:04,220 --> 00:16:06,620
你现在竟然还没下台
And you're still in charge.

298
00:16:06,660 --> 00:16:07,700
如果我们不让这样的
If we can't remove

299
00:16:07,700 --> 00:16:09,330
所谓的管理者下台的话 戴安娜
our so-called leaders, Diana,

300
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:11,490
就是放任法西斯主义
we're staring fascism in the face.

301
00:16:11,530 --> 00:16:13,230
您是法西斯吗 长官?
Are you a fascist, inspector?

302
00:16:13,260 --> 00:16:15,330
在奈杰尔的眼中 我就是个公司的走狗而已
According to Nigel, I'm a corporate lackey.

303
00:16:15,370 --> 00:16:17,700
但我觉得这两种形象有点矛盾
It seems contradictory to me.

304
00:16:21,740 --> 00:16:25,770
问得好
Excellent question.

305
00:16:25,810 --> 00:16:28,080
比平时有进步啊
That was better than usual.

306
00:16:30,610 --> 00:16:32,850
切断信号
Kill the feed.

307
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:37,300
他们堵住了大门 在门上安了炸药
They blocked and booby-trapped the doors.

308
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:38,740
大部分员工都被赶出来了
Most of the staff were forced out

309
00:16:38,770 --> 00:16:41,410
里面还有狄龙局长和其他八个人质
except for inspector Dillon and eight other hostages.

310
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,570
