你的内线最近很安静啊
Your contact's gone quiet.

319
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:02,190
没有她我们能行吗?
Can we still do this without her?

320
00:17:02,230 --> 00:17:05,130
别担心 我会有办法的
Trust me, I'll find a way.

321
00:17:08,830 --> 00:17:11,240
其实我们都知道现在的状况
We know how this plays.

322
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:13,940
你们的人在外面一边封锁街道
Your troops are outside shutting down streets,

323
00:17:13,970 --> 00:17:17,140
一边想方设法找其他的入口
searching for entries into the building from above and below.

324
00:17:17,170 --> 00:17:18,710
你在每个入口都安装了炸弹
You've wired all entries to blow,

325
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:20,840
