355
00:18:28,010 --> 00:18:29,340
这没道理啊
It doesn't make sense.

356
00:18:29,380 --> 00:18:31,750
过去 当卡加梅和卢卡斯想要宣传他们的理念
In the past, when Kagame and Lucas wanted to reach people

