We negotiate for Dillon.

369
00:18:51,870 --> 00:18:54,170
人质是不分三六九等的
There are no VIP's in a hostage situation.

370
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,540
如果是我在里面 狄龙在外面负责解救人质
If I was in there and Dillon was out here,

371
00:18:55,570 --> 00:18:58,570
他会跟我做一样的决定的
he would make exactly the same call.

372
00:18:58,610 --> 00:19:00,410
让电力公司伪造一个变压器故障
Have hydro stage a transformer failure,

373
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:02,480
告诉他们因为这个原因不能直播
tell them that's why they're off the air.

374
00:19:02,510 --> 00:19:03,840
这个说法骗不了他们多长时间
It won't convince them for long.

375
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:04,850
我们也不需要多长时间
We don't need that long,

376
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,480
够你们找到入口就行了
just long enough for you to export this entry.

377
00:19:06,510 --> 00:19:09,650
带两个人 摸清状况
Take two guys, see what you can find.

378
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:11,480
你也要进去
You're going in there also.

379
00:19:11,520 --> 00:19:12,250
跟他们一起?
With them?

380
00:19:12,290 --> 00:19:13,250
不
No.

381
00:19:13,290 --> 00:19:15,860
用你的方式进去 好吗?
Do that thing that you do, ok?

382
00:19:15,890 --> 00:19:18,020
随时保持联系
Keep a line open for me.

383
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:23,600
琪拉
Kiera.

384
00:19:23,630 --> 00:19:25,100
我们要救的是所有的人质
We want to rescue all of them.

385
00:19:25,130 --> 00:19:28,170
知道了
I know.

386
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:29,740
现在有两个人已经...
We have a two man team...

387
00:19:35,610 --> 00:19:37,180
看来好戏已经开始了
They're starting to play their games.

388
00:19:37,210 --> 00:19:40,310
没事 我临时找了个备用电源
It doesn't matter, I rigged a back-up circuit.

389
00:19:40,350 --> 00:19:44,580
马上就好 三 二 一
It should activate in three... two... one.

390
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:48,450
在我们得到卫星系统的代码之前
It's the only magic trick I've got

391
00:19:48,490 --> 00:19:50,590
我只能做到这一步了
until we get those satellite codes.

392
00:19:55,260 --> 00:19:57,460
今天对你来说真的很忙啊
Busy day for you.

393
00:19:57,500 --> 00:20:02,500
逮捕你自己的女儿 在电视节目上道貌岸然
Arrest your own daughter, act the righteous man on TV,

394
00:20:02,530 --> 00:20:04,400
现在又被当人质给抓起来了
get taken hostage.

395
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:07,440
晚上的运气有点不好
Tonight can only be a let down.

396
00:20:07,470 --> 00:20:09,840
你到底想要什么?
What do you want?

397
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:16,310
你觉得我想要什么?
What do you think I want?

398
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:17,820
你一直想抓住我
You've been chasing me long enough.

399
00:20:17,850 --> 00:20:20,150
你喜欢扯一大堆解放人民的鬼话
You know, you talk a great game about freeing the people,

400
00:20:20,190 --> 00:20:22,190
但一到你身上
but it's on your terms.

401
00:20:22,220 --> 00:20:23,660
要是有人跟你意见不合...
Anybody who doesn't agree with you...

402
00:20:23,690 --> 00:20:26,690
就会被老爸抓起来
Ends up being arrested by daddy.

403
00:20:34,970 --> 00:20:36,970
你当不了英雄 局长
You're not that guy, inspector.

404
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:41,110
你拿不到那把枪的 也无法扭转局势
You're not getting the gun, you're not saving the day.

405
00:20:41,140 --> 00:20:43,010
看来你很自信啊?
Pretty confident in that, are you?

406
00:20:43,040 --> 00:20:44,180
我是很自信
I am.

407
00:20:44,210 --> 00:20:46,610
很好
Great.

408
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:49,950
福乃格最好能给我想要的东西
Your boy Fonnegra better get me what I want.

409
00:20:49,980 --> 00:20:53,080
我十分赞同你的想法 贝尔塔先生
I'm in agreement with your principles, Mr. Verta.

410
00:20:53,120 --> 00:20:56,150
要限制正在增长的公司企业的权力
Strip the power away from this growing corporate mono-culture.

411
00:20:56,190 --> 00:20:57,890
闭嘴  奈杰尔 别乱说话
Shut up, Nigel, you're encouraging a terrorist!

412
00:20:57,920 --> 00:21:00,360
只有解放组织看清了 如果我们不反抗
Liber8 has the only clear vision of what lies ahead

413
00:21:00,390 --> 00:21:02,330
未来的下场会怎样
if we don't speak up.

414
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:04,330
贝尔塔先生和他的朋友们
Mr. Verta and his friends here

415
00:21:04,360 --> 00:21:05,090
就是未来唯一的希望
are the only hope for the future.

416
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:12,140
别再乱说话
No more talking heads.

417
00:21:12,170 --> 00:21:14,040
别担心 死不了
Oh, he'll live.

418
00:21:14,070 --> 00:21:16,710
还能坚持一会儿
For a while.

419
00:21:16,740 --> 00:21:19,480
你们肯定很想去帮他止血吧
You might want to block up that hole.

420
00:21:19,510 --> 00:21:22,080
你别动
Not you.

421
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:26,870
当我看你的节目的时候
When I watch your show,

422
00:21:26,870 --> 00:21:28,620
我真为你感到羞愧
I'm ashamed for you.

423
00:21:28,650 --> 00:21:31,590
为你的观众感到羞愧
For all your viewers.

424
00:21:31,620 --> 00:21:33,990
没有思想 没有分析
No awareness, no analysis,

425
00:21:33,990 --> 00:21:37,160
有的只是些翻动言论
just reactionary opinions.

426
00:21:37,190 --> 00:21:39,960
节目做成这样 你也有责任
You are part of the problem.

427
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:44,700
不过你只是一个漂亮的傀儡罢了
A pretty, empty puppet.

428
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:48,700
只会带着一群人嬉笑作乐
Leading everyone on a merry dance.

429
00:21:53,840 --> 00:21:57,980
告诉福乃格他没有多少时间了
Tell Fonnegra he doesn't have much time.

430
00:21:59,520 --> 00:22:00,980
特拉维斯?
Travis?

431
00:22:24,600 --> 00:22:26,200
所有人质都还活着吗?
Are all the hostages still alive?

432
00:22:26,610 --> 00:22:29,340
是的 但是时间不多了
For now, but the clock is ticking.

433
00:22:29,370 --> 00:22:32,280
十五分钟之内给我接通卫星服务
Full access to those satellites in 15 minutes

434
00:22:32,310 --> 00:22:35,710
不然我就杀了博尔顿小姐 表明下我的决心
or I'll shoot Miss Bolton next as a sign of my resolve.

435
00:22:35,750 --> 00:22:38,520
特拉维斯 我们在解决你代码的事
Travis, we're working on getting you the codes,

436
00:22:38,550 --> 00:22:39,520
但是这需要一点时间
but it's slow going.

437
00:22:39,550 --> 00:22:40,820
公司不愿意交出代码
The company doesn't want to give them up.

438
00:22:40,850 --> 00:22:43,750
别跟我来谈判这一套 福乃格
Save the negotiator clich, Fonnegra.

439
00:22:43,790 --> 00:22:47,120
拖延战术只会导致
Stalling is only going to lead to something...

440
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:49,360
无法挽回的结果
Terminal.

441
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:55,930
喂
Yeah.

442
00:22:55,970 --> 00:22:57,430
我进来了
I'm in.

443
00:22:57,470 --> 00:22:58,400
很好
Alright, good.

444
00:22:58,440 --> 00:22:59,940
随时跟我联系
Keep me apprise step by step.

445
00:22:59,970 --> 00:23:02,270
知道了
Roger that.

446
00:23:02,310 --> 00:23:03,410
我想我知道为什么电视台
I think I know why the network

447
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:05,670
不把卫星交出来
isn't releasing access to the satellites.

448
00:23:05,710 --> 00:23:09,310
2010年整个公司已经被弗门塔斯公司买下了
That whole conglomerate was bought out in 2010 by Fermitas.

449
00:23:09,350 --> 00:23:11,180
第一频道被军火商买下了?
The weapons-maker owns Channel 1?

450
00:23:11,220 --> 00:23:13,620
戴安娜·博尔顿几年前曾经
Diana Bolton ran a huge expose on Fermitas

451
00:23:13,650 --> 00:23:15,320
要曝光弗门塔斯的内幕
a couple years ago.

452
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:17,420
弗门塔斯声称要控告她
Fermitas announced an intention to sue,

453
00:23:17,450 --> 00:23:18,820
之后又不告了
then dropped the suit.

454
00:23:18,860 --> 00:23:20,490
人们当时以为是因为赢不了
People figured it was because it wasn't winnable,

455
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:21,720
但是事实是
but really...

456
00:23:21,760 --> 00:23:23,130
如果你不能封锁媒体 就把它们买下来
If you can't muzzle the press, you buy them.

457
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:25,290
将其私下收购
Private acquisition.

458
00:23:25,330 --> 00:23:27,100
私下收购?
Private acquisition?

459
00:23:27,130 --> 00:23:29,460
这么说没人知道?
So nobody knows?

460
00:23:29,500 --> 00:23:31,670
卢卡斯也许知道了
Lucas might have found out.

461
00:23:31,700 --> 00:23:32,700
是吗?
Did he?

462
00:23:32,740 --> 00:23:35,000
不是我告诉他的 我发誓
Not from me, I swear it.

463
00:23:38,970 --> 00:23:40,210
你现在在哪呢?
What's your twenty?

464
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:43,610
监控室 看特拉维斯和卢卡斯在楼里扫荡呢
Security room, watching Travis and Lucas storm the castle.

465
00:23:43,650 --> 00:23:46,080
所有这一切就为了在电视上播出他们的宣言?
All this effort to broadcast a manifesto?

466
00:23:46,120 --> 00:23:47,980
嗯 这还有条爆炸新闻等着你呢
Well, here's some breaking news for ya.

467
00:23:48,020 --> 00:23:50,420
弗门塔斯是这家电视台的幕后老板
Fermitas owns the station.

468
00:23:50,450 --> 00:23:51,850
私人收购买卖
Private buying private.

469
00:23:51,890 --> 00:23:53,450
那些保险箱
The safety deposit boxes.

470
00:23:53,490 --> 00:23:56,390
解放组织就是这么发现这笔交易的
That's how Liber8 found out about the sale.

471
00:23:56,430 --> 00:23:58,290
加尔萨和索尼娅不在
Garza and Sonya aren't here.

472
00:23:58,330 --> 00:23:59,990
什么 兵分两路 分头进攻?
What, two-prong attack?

473
00:24:00,030 --> 00:24:00,900
有道理
Makes sense.

474
00:24:00,930 --> 00:24:01,760
卡洛斯?
Carlos?

475
00:24:01,800 --> 00:24:03,300
保持联系
Stay in touch.

476
00:24:03,330 --> 00:24:04,600
我们遇到问题了
We have a problem.

477
00:24:04,630 --> 00:24:06,200
我的人已经进去了但是到演播室的
My men are inside but access to the studio

478
00:24:06,230 --> 00:24:08,170
门被装上了炸药
is rigged with explosives.

479
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:09,370
拆弹小组呢?
Bomb squad?

480
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:10,500
我们从来没见过这种东西
We've never seen anything like this.

481
00:24:10,540 --> 00:24:13,170
长官 企业集团代表来了
Sir, the corporate rep is here.

482
00:24:13,210 --> 00:24:15,310
稍等我一下
Give me a second.

483
00:24:17,710 --> 00:24:18,480
你是本尼迪克特?
You Benedict?

484
00:24:18,510 --> 00:24:19,750
是的
Yes.

485
00:24:19,780 --> 00:24:21,650
弗门塔斯的?
Fermitas?

486
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:22,380
是的
Yes.

487
00:24:22,420 --> 00:24:23,420
太好了
Good.

488
00:24:23,450 --> 00:24:24,650
他们已经枪伤了一人除非我们能满足
One man has been shot and there will be others

489
00:24:24,690 --> 00:24:27,590
解放组织的部分要求 否则其他人也有危险了
unless we give Liber8 at least part of what they demanded.

490
00:24:27,620 --> 00:24:30,920
恐怖组织想要连接电视台卫星的代码
Terrorists want the codes to the station's satellite.

491
00:24:30,960 --> 00:24:33,130
抱歉 警探 但是公司有着严格的规定
Detective, I'm sorry, that company has a strict policy

492
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:35,230
禁止和恐怖分子谈判
against negotiating with terrorists.

493
00:24:35,260 --> 00:24:39,000
所以你非常高兴能成为谋杀犯的帮凶?
So you're perfectly content with being accomplices to murder?

494
00:24:39,030 --> 00:24:42,440
这家电视台也是弗门塔斯的 是不是?
That is Fermitas's business, isn't it?

495
00:24:42,470 --> 00:24:45,140
我不想浪费你的时间
I don't want to waste your time.

496
00:24:46,410 --> 00:24:50,110
解放组织至少拿到了弗门塔斯的一个保险箱
Liber8 emptied at least one Fermitas safety deposit box.

497
00:24:50,140 --> 00:24:51,310
这也许是你们把里面的情报
This could be an opportunity

498
00:24:51,350 --> 00:24:53,350
拿回来的好机会
for you to retrieve that information.

499
00:24:53,380 --> 00:24:56,180
否则 不论里面是什么
Otherwise, Liber8 still has

500
00:24:56,180 --> 00:24:59,490
东西依然掌握在解放组织手里
whatever it is that you lost,

501
00:24:59,520 --> 00:25:00,890
而他们会好好利用的
and they will use it.

502
00:25:06,190 --> 00:25:07,660
就好像在下鱼饵一样
It's like baiting a hook.

503
00:25:07,690 --> 00:25:11,160
是啊 我们有麻烦了 他们不会善罢甘休的
Yeah, we got a problem, they're not gonna go for it.

504
00:25:35,090 --> 00:25:37,820
把我留下放其他人走
You keep me as collateral and everybody else walks.

505
00:25:39,990 --> 00:25:41,820
锁定目标

506
00:25:43,500 --> 00:25:45,660
不可能
No deal.

507
00:25:54,110 --> 00:25:57,640
局长 你觉得接下来会怎样?
What do you think happens next, inspector?

508
00:26:10,620 --> 00:26:12,090
特拉维斯 出什么事情了?
What's happening, Travis?

509
00:26:12,120 --> 00:26:13,460
不是什么好事
Nothing good.

510
00:26:13,490 --> 00:26:14,290
卫星
The satellite.

511
00:26:14,330 --> 00:26:15,930
你可以用了
You have access.

512
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:21,200
转发器的代码正在发给你
Transponder codes are being fed to you now.

513
00:26:21,230 --> 00:26:23,600
谎言中的又一天
Live to lie another day.

514
00:26:36,110 --> 00:26:37,510
你没事吧?
You ok?

515
00:26:37,550 --> 00:26:39,320
不 我感觉很不好
No, I'm not.

516
00:26:39,350 --> 00:26:41,920
我甚至在为奈杰尔感到难过
I even feel badly for Nigel.

517
00:26:41,950 --> 00:26:44,290
所以我知道我现在糟糕透了
That's how I know I'm a wreck.

518
00:26:44,320 --> 00:26:45,490
好了
Good to go.

519
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:48,760
重新设置卫星需要二十分钟
Re-tasking the satellite will take 20 minutes.

520
00:26:55,830 --> 00:26:59,000
准备直播 三 二 ...
We're live in three... Two...

521
00:27:02,470 --> 00:27:05,040
你们中的很多人觉得认识我
Most of you think you know me.

522
00:27:05,070 --> 00:27:06,710
特拉维斯·贝尔塔
Travis Verta.

523
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:08,010
解放组织
Liber8.

524
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:09,410
杀人犯
Killer.

525
00:27:09,450 --> 00:27:10,850
恐怖分子
Terrorist.

526
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:12,610
疯子
Lunatic.

527
00:27:12,650 --> 00:27:16,990
现我又在这打断你们的节目
And now here I am, interrupting your programming.

528
00:27:17,020 --> 00:27:21,220
这样的节目必须被打断
That's some programming that needs to be interrupted.

529
00:27:21,260 --> 00:27:25,490
我们过去拥有的公司 现在拥有了我们
Companies we used to own, own us.

530
00:27:25,530 --> 00:27:28,800
以前我们选出的政府 现在被收买
Governments that used to be voted in, are bought.

531
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:30,670
而可以用来曝光这些的
And a supposedly "free press"

532
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:32,730
所谓自由媒体
who could expose all this

533
00:27:32,770 --> 00:27:37,170
现在都被这些企业集团所拥有
are now owned by these very corporations.

534
00:27:37,210 --> 00:27:41,280
我们孩子们的自由生活岌岌可危
Our children's lives are at stake.

535
00:27:41,310 --> 00:27:43,210
未来即将到来
The future is coming.

536
00:27:43,250 --> 00:27:45,580
而他们只被要求做一件事
It wants only one thing from them:

537
00:27:45,610 --> 00:27:46,780
就是绝对服从
Obedience.

538
00:27:46,820 --> 00:27:48,850
看起来不太好啊
That doesn't look good.

539
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:50,120
是不妙
It's not.

540
00:27:50,150 --> 00:27:53,020
卢卡斯在里面加入了2077年才有的一些成分
Lucas added some 2077 into the equation.
炸药

541
00:27:53,050 --> 00:27:54,720
艾力克 你的出现刚刚好
Alec, your timing couldn't be better.

542
00:27:54,760 --> 00:27:57,790
能用赛德科技的服务器搜索一下简单爆炸装置
Can you have the Sadtech servers run an IED bomb search,

543
00:27:57,830 --> 00:27:59,290
起爆电路...
firing schematics...

544
00:27:59,330 --> 00:28:04,130
我现在在派朗的办公室里
I'm in my office at Piron.

545
00:28:04,170 --> 00:28:05,170
哦 当然
Of course.

546
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,330
当然是了
Of course you are.

547
00:28:06,370 --> 00:28:09,940
你以为我是另一个我 是吗?
You thought I was other me, didn't you?

548
00:28:09,970 --> 00:28:11,610
你早就知道了
You knew.

549
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:13,130
我还希望你不知道
I was hoping you didn't,

550
00:28:13,130 --> 00:28:15,940
不过你这样我一点都不惊讶
but I wish I was surprised.

551
00:28:15,980 --> 00:28:18,610
艾力克 我需要保护你
Alec, I needed to protect you,

552
00:28:18,650 --> 00:28:20,150
我以为这是最好的
and I thought this was the best...

553
00:28:20,180 --> 00:28:21,750
每个人都在努力的保护我
